*$.HE ISD GENERALIZED SUBROUTINES - SYSCLOS
*$.HE PLI INTERFACE TO CLOSE MACRO
*$.PL 55
*$.PN 0
*$.PA
*$.SS
*$.NF
*$12/1/76
*$AUTHOR:  T. SMITH
*$SOURCE MODULE NAME:  SYSCLOS
*$DOCUMENTATION ID:  *$
*$.FI L
*$.SP 5
*$THIS ROUTINE PROVIDES THE PLI PROGRAMMER WITH AN INTERFACE TO THE
*$CLOSE MACRO.
*$.SP 1
*$.IN 5
*$CALL SYSCLOS(DCBPTR);
*$.SP 1
*$.IN 0
*$DCBPTR IS A POINTER VARIABLE SET TO THE ADDRESS OF THE DCB TO BE
*$CLOSED.  THIS POINTER VARIABLE SHOULD HAVE BEEN SET BY A PREVIOUS
*$CALL TO SYSDCBP.
SYSCLOS  PLIENTRY ,DSA=108
         L     R2,0(R1)                R2 = A(DCBPTR)
         L     R2,0(R2)                R2 = A(DCB)
         LA    R1,LIST
         MVI   LIST,X'80'
         CLOSE ((2),DISP),MF=(E,(1))
         PLIEXIT
         LTORG
DSA      DSECT
LIST     DS    F
         END
